de.fhg.fit.biomos.sensorplatform.persistence

Class DBsession

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.fhg.fit.biomos.sensorplatform.persistence.DBsession

  • public class DBsession
extends Object
    Exposes basic functions for database interaction. It is instantiated by the DBcontroller (factory). Use one DBsession for one database interaction and throw it away afterwards.
    Author:
    Daniel Pyka
